item.title: Pemimpin.ID Mentorship Program
item.description: A mentorship program focused on empowering young leaders with the necessary skills to positively impact their communities through workshops, training sessions, and one-on-one mentorship.

item.title: Generasi Bebas Plastik
item.description: A community-driven project focused on reducing plastic waste by educating and engaging local communities. It involves workshops, awareness campaigns, and collaboration with local waste management systems.

item.title: Laundry Management System - UI/UX Design with Figma
item.description: Created an intuitive and user-friendly interface for the Laundry Management System using Figma. The design focused on simplicity and easy navigation, ensuring a seamless user experience for customers managing their laundry services.
